{"tid":2393817,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[有錢上天堂] 播道會擁8億九龍塘靚地 牧師叫教友借錢還3億債","createTime":"2021-02-03T17:54:58.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-09T05:28:00.000Z","uid":224066,"like":5,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"6bed8d9e036b255ccf15931abb2f0774e71c23e9","tid":2393817,"uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T17:54:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/2rgMzW4aE7PIbTg8n7AC6vLd510=/802x459/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/LXDCXRAFUZDT7OFD65P6IOPIJE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F2rgMzW4aE7PIbTg8n7AC6vLd510%3D%2F802x459%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FLXDCXRAFUZDT7OFD65P6IOPIJE.jpg&h=5ca19537&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港基督教播道會聯會賬目混亂，2018年財務報表聲稱現金結餘只有44萬元，同年斥資3.2億元購入港大校舍作神學院用途。近月高層發公開信，指買校舍衍生赤字高達3.8億元，每月支付銀行60萬元利息，呼籲教友提供無息貸款或無償奉獻協助還債。不過，聯會實際家底豐厚，擁有3幅九龍塘地皮，共值近8億元。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/i_BAWOdLT4qQ0lVYqTuhdFCK_hs=/802x534/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/WKKZN7EVZ5COHDCCWWK6NU5GFA.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fi_BAWOdLT4qQ0lVYqTuhdFCK_hs%3D%2F802x534%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FWKKZN7EVZ5COHDCCWWK6NU5GFA.JPG&h=a3d108d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Nz5LIU9buP20Tw_t32FGyXbC-Dk=/802x501/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/DBD7BRVJLZFWDM2NZDLCAUILGI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FNz5LIU9buP20Tw_t32FGyXbC-Dk%3D%2F802x501%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FDBD7BRVJLZFWDM2NZDLCAUILGI.jpg&h=6e174099&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n陳黔開兩個多月前以播道神學院院董會主席身份發信，呼籲教友提供免息貸款助還債。<br />\n<br />\n根據稅務局資料，聯會在1957年成立，登記成為慈善團體，有67個附屬機構，<span class=\"red\">包括恩泉堂、同福堂、雅斤堂和播道神學院等。</span>翻查2019年財務報表，聯會主席是蘇振豪，而社聯公開資料顯示，副主席是陳黔開牧師。陳黔開亦同時擔任多個基督教團體的顧問，<span class=\"red\">包括城市睦福團契、基督教互愛中心，及警隊「以諾團契」等。</span><br />\n<br />\n聯會規模龐大，但報稱的資產和收入少得離奇。2018年周年財務報表報稱收入不足8萬元，主要是聯會會費，而現金結餘僅44萬元、總資產505萬元。不過，負責財務報表的核數師披露，聯會以信託形式代聯會會員持有物業和上司公司股票，部份物業已抵押，但財務報表一直無交代物業、抵押貸款、股票、租金和財務擔保合約。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/ZJQ_oZLel_mq7-Z4pqdJKVjxhBM=/802x393/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/N35XZC6J2REEXNUIKPEMBZMEYM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FZJQ_oZLel_mq7-Z4pqdJKVjxhBM%3D%2F802x393%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FN35XZC6J2REEXNUIKPEMBZMEYM.jpg&h=c309a8b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n核數師最近3年對財務報表持保留意見（Qualified opinion），認為聯會無按照《公司條例》和會計師公會準則編製財務報表。香港會計手足工會主席吳浩謙指，「保留意見」意味會計師對賬目有懷疑，「我哋會計師角度，佢盤數有問題，我哋畀唔到clean opinion（無保留意見）佢。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/V0_-cuPeIO7pBilXU2t0ZW7iazM=/802x491/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/VBPNRC7KYRBQPCXZDTV763VNGI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FV0_-cuPeIO7pBilXU2t0ZW7iazM%3D%2F802x491%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FVBPNRC7KYRBQPCXZDTV763VNGI.jpg&h=90ef3696&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n聯會報稱資產極少，卻在2018年斥資3.24億元購入香港大學在美孚的教學中心，用作播道神學院新校舍。吳浩謙認為，交易金額與報表上資產不相稱，「我點睇呢？佢都冇乜可能用43萬（現金）買到以億計嘅嘢。」此外，2019年報表亦未見相關銀行借貸或資產入賬，「其實應該反映喺財務報告度，例如佢借幾多錢、佢借（嘅）期限，例如利息係幾多。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/oXlfzlY1-yh8CiIlzBSROdm93d4=/802x526/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/7GYBSJ7EHJBYTA3M6F5LQTAIUE.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FoXlfzlY1-yh8CiIlzBSROdm93d4%3D%2F802x526%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F7GYBSJ7EHJBYTA3M6F5LQTAIUE.JPG&h=dbb5ac2d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n記者查冊發現，聯會在購入美孚校舍前一日，將3塊九龍塘地皮連物業抵押予銀行，估計是借貸用途。根據聯會披露，買校舍費用連同稅金、裝修費，總成本高達4.5億元。《蘋果》委託泓亮諮詢及評估有限公司估值，美孚校舍最新市值估計約2.8億元。換言之，3年間賬面已蝕約1.7億元。泓亮董事總經理張翹楚解釋，本港整體商業物業市場疲弱，美孚屬民生區域，跌幅已經算較少。<br />\n翻查資料，九龍塘在2018年至2020年逾10宗地皮成交，由1億元至7億元不等。本報委託估值聯會持有的3塊九龍塘地皮，得出總值約7.73億元。張翹楚分析，有關地皮可做商業用途或住宅用途，屬優質地段，可考慮招標發售，吸引買家報價，只要售出其中一塊地皮，已可套現逾2億元。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/VW86F5qoYYu08I9sEj9XrbrsrBw=/802x532/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/XUNIOVEUNBE5TCTR7MO7MSYWRM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FVW86F5qoYYu08I9sEj9XrbrsrBw%3D%2F802x532%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FXUNIOVEUNBE5TCTR7MO7MSYWRM.jpg&h=3789522a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/fqIqL1TVXlyt5GOpEJB2SX-b-MM=/802x532/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/VRSIDUFPSZBVFJOD2L457XS77U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FfqIqL1TVXlyt5GOpEJB2SX-b-MM%3D%2F802x532%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FVRSIDUFPSZBVFJOD2L457XS77U.jpg&h=40f01fe6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Xe0AUUP3XbZ6dPyybjXk6eXifv8=/802x532/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/NU43VHSSYJEBDAGWE7JIQQHZ3U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FXe0AUUP3XbZ6dPyybjXk6eXifv8%3D%2F802x532%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FNU43VHSSYJEBDAGWE7JIQQHZ3U.jpg&h=4009a904&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n播道會聯會回覆《蘋果》指，過去兩年香港經濟困難，拖延出售物業步伐，神學院因為周轉困難，向弟兄姐妹請求免息貸款，成功出售舊校舍後，會按計劃還清銀行貸款和教友貸款。聯會承認，在處理所有堂會會計報表合併工作上，未能按核數師的時間完成，因此最近3年財務報表獲評「保留意見」"},{"pid":"e5312a352e2d28654e8873b7d353d2d867ee82ef","tid":2393817,"uid":199670,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T17:56:09.000Z","msg":"周轉問題啫"},{"pid":"c88237a8397fcfbeddabd37ff4a340fbe43631ad","tid":2393817,"uid":48967,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T18:07:38.000Z","msg":"乜鳩野 同行肢體們 肢體<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4405d8de0efaaaf826e05f0deed5095b28b6161d","tid":2393817,"uid":276273,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T18:15:15.000Z","msg":"上帝比你既試煉，自己搞掂佢啦，完。"},{"pid":"628ec9a49a6446d86ab3a28cffc2e3fe886facd6","tid":2393817,"uid":65063,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T18:25:02.000Z","msg":"淨係句「受社會事件影響」已經想推到佢仆街"},{"pid":"8de039373cc846938d5734608f113d10d8b05463","tid":2393817,"uid":23277,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c88237a8397fcfbeddabd37ff4a340fbe43631ad","tid":2393817,"uid":48967,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T18:07:38.000Z","msg":"乜鳩野 同行肢體們 肢體<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T18:33:52.000Z","msg":"係咪即係手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"522dda47c6d6b2591d2965eb60e0dc63b59ec1a1","tid":2393817,"uid":89641,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T00:10:48.000Z","msg":"呢個藍屍教會, 自己申請遮仔會都得啦!"},{"pid":"9110a75384895e162b1dd957b9349965e96b60f3","tid":2393817,"uid":89861,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T00:24:40.000Z","msg":"教會只係一盤生意"},{"pid":"34405d9e9861f0430f